{"type":null,"faqId":45347,"title":"荣耀盒子M321的遥控器反应迟钝，先失去响应，过一段时间后连续响应怎么办？","answer":"<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\r\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\r\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\r\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\r\n</style>\n<div>\n<p><span>\"1. 请进入“设置 &gt; 版本升级”将盒子升级到最新版本。新版本已改善该问题。<br>\n2. 请先暂停节目缓存。节目缓存会占用网络带宽和内存，可能会延迟盒子对遥控器的响应。<br>\n3. 请按遥控器待机键，清理内存。<br>\n4. 请将盒子断电重启（需拔掉电源线）。\" <br>\n</span></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":246,"faqType":"遥控","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"868","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Remote","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442556875000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M321,MediaQ M321-20","visitedTimes":23,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"反应迟钝,没响应,连续响应,荣耀盒子","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}